      "اَللّٰهُمَّ لَقِّنِىْ حُجَّتِىْ يَوْمَ اَلْقَاكَ",
      "وَاَطْلِقْ لِسَانِىْ بِذِكْرِاكَ"
    ],
    "translation": [
      "O Lord! Dictate to me the principles of faith on the Day I meet You,",
      "and make my tongue fluent with Your remembrance."
